# Obsidian / vault directories that appear if VAULT_PATH points at the repo
# (e.g. someone runs `contextvault init` here by mistake). The real vault
# lives in ~/Documents/ContextVault — these should never enter version control.
.obsidian/
workspaces/
entities/
concepts/
hot.md
index.md
log.md

# Obsidian plugin build output
obsidian-plugin/main.js
obsidian-plugin/node_modules/
obsidian-plugin/*.tgz

# Test artifacts
tests/tmp/
